---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Tim & Katie Graves — Graves Properties | NH Renovation Contractor"
  description="Tim and Katie Graves have been renovating, flipping, and managing rental properties across New Hampshire for over 10 years. Seacoast-based, hands-on, husband-and-wife team."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sky-400 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Who We Are</p>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight mb-5">
          We're Tim + Katie,<br>
          <span class="text-sky-400">NH Renovators</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg mb-4">
          We've been buying, renovating, and managing New Hampshire properties for over
          ten years — together. We're not a corporation or a fund. When you work with
          Graves Properties, you get one of us.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-base">
          We started with a beat-up duplex fresh out of college and we haven't stopped since.
          This is what we do — and we genuinely love it.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-slate-700 rounded-2xl aspect-[4/5] flex items-center justify-center">
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Tim & Katie photo</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR STORY -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-slate-900 mb-6">How It Started</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-5 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We bought our first property right out of college — a duplex that needed everything.
        We renovated it together, and somewhere between ripping out old floors and
        painting every room twice, we became a couple. That house brought us together
        in more ways than one.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-5 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Since then, we've fix-and-flipped across New Hampshire, managed rentals from the
        Keene area all the way to the seacoast, and tackled more projects than we can
        easily count. One of our favorites: we moved into a flip the day after closing —
        because we found out we were having our first baby girl and needed a place to
        call home fast. No regrets.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-5 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We own rentals across the state but we're seacoast-based now, headquartered
        out of Stratham. New Hampshire is home — not a market we're investing in from
        afar. We're here, our kids are growing up here, and the homes we work on
        are in the same communities we care about.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TIM + KATIE SKILLS -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-slate-900 text-center mb-4">We Do the Work Ourselves</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        When we walk through a property, we're not guessing. We've done this work with
        our own hands on dozens of homes — that's why our renovations hold up and our
        timelines are real.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sky-100 text-sky-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17L17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0021 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 11-3.586-3.586l6.837-5.63m5.108-.233c.55-.164 1.163-.188 1.743-.14a4.5 4.5 0 004.486-6.336l-3.276 3.277a3.004 3.004 0 01-2.25-2.25l3.276-3.276a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.336 4.486c.091 1.076-.071 2.264-.904 2.95l-.102.085"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-slate-900 mb-3">Tim</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Tim handles the structural side — framing, flooring, cabinets, and trim.
            He can walk into a house and mentally pull it apart and put it back together
            before he's made it to the kitchen. That's how we scope projects accurately
            and keep renovations on budget.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sky-100 text-sky-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.53 16.122a3 3 0 00-5.78 1.128 2.25 2.25 0 01-2.4 2.245 4.5 4.5 0 008.4-2.245c0-.399-.078-.78-.22-1.128zm0 0a15.998 15.998 0 003.388-1.62m-5.043-.025a15.994 15.994 0 011.622-3.395m3.42 3.42a15.995 15.995 0 004.764-4.648l3.876-5.814a1.151 1.151 0 00-1.597-1.597L14.146 6.32a15.996 15.996 0 00-4.649 4.763m3.42 3.42a6.776 6.776 0 00-3.42-3.42"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-slate-900 mb-3">Katie</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Katie is the finish expert — mud, tape, caulking, and painting.
            She's the reason every property we touch looks like a home, not a job site.
            She also has an instinct for what a space could become that drives every
            design decision. Their partnership — in work and in life — is what
            makes Graves Properties run.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT DRIVES US -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-slate-900 mb-6">Why We Do This</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-5 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We love bringing properties back to life. There's something deeply satisfying about
        walking into a house that's been neglected or has had a hard few years, and
        seeing what it could be. That's always been the core of it for us.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-5 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Whether we're flipping a property, building out a rental, or taking on a
        full gut renovation, the mission is the same: do excellent work on homes
        that deserve it. We live in these communities, our kids go to school here,
        and we take pride in the properties we put back into the housing stock.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        That's it, really. Good people, good homes, good work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW WE WORK -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-slate-900 text-center mb-12">How We Work</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sky-100 text-sky-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.036 12.322a1.012 1.012 0 010-.639C3.423 7.51 7.36 4.5 12 4.5c4.638 0 8.573 3.007 9.963 7.178.07.207.07.431 0 .639C20.577 16.49 16.64 19.5 12 19.5c-4.638 0-8.573-3.007-9.963-7.178z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">Transparent</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We're upfront about timelines, budgets, and what a project actually needs. No surprises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sky-100 text-sky-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">Quality-First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We don't cut corners. Every renovation — whether it's a flip or a rental — is done to the same standard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sky-100 text-sky-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">Local</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We live in Stratham, work statewide, and care about the NH communities we build in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-slate-900 mb-4">Where We Work</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          We renovate, flip, and manage rentals throughout New Hampshire. We're most active on
          the <strong class="text-slate-900">seacoast</strong> and in
          <strong class="text-slate-900">Rockingham and Strafford Counties</strong>,
          but we take on projects statewide.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Portsmouth</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Manchester</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Dover</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Exeter</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Rochester</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Derry</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Hampton</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Concord</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Keene</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Nashua</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> Stratham</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-sky-600">&#10003;</span> And more&#8230;</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-3">Reach Out Directly</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-5">
          Have a property to discuss? Interested in a rental? Call or text Tim directly.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <a href="tel:+16037852811"
             class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:border-sky-400 transition-colors no-underline">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Call or Text</p>
              <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">603-785-2811</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:tim@nhgraves.com"
             class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:border-sky-400 transition-colors no-underline">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Email</p>
              <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">tim@nhgraves.com</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BEST NH REALTY CROSS-LINK -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-3">Need to Sell Your Home Fast?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">
        Through Best NH Realty, we also buy houses directly for cash — any condition, fast closings, zero commissions.
      </p>
      <a href="https://bestnhrealty.com"
         class="inline-block bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl no-underline transition-colors">
        Visit Best NH Realty &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
